cc / clientcommand            Adds a client command to the current recording

   Format:
      ;cc <cmd>               Adds a client command

   Notes:
      Adds a client command to the current recording, which will be automically
         removed later (unless the recording is saved as a mission).
      (If you need to preserve spacing, enclose the command with diamond
          brackets <...>)
      See the help for the ';record' command for more information about
         recordings.

   User commands:
      cc / clientcmd / clientcommand
